- LVM2 (2020-02-18)

### Mounting for chroot (Arch ISO)
- modprobe dm_mod
- vgscan
- vgchange -ay
- lvdisplay
- mkdir -vp /mnt/centos/{root,home}
- mount <LV_PATH> /mnt/centos/root
- mount <LV_PATH> /mnt/centos/home
- chroot /mnt/centos/root
- Don't forget to umount /mnt/centos/root when finished
